{"tid":1444773,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(呼籲)全部手足11點前返晒屋企!! 黑警戰術已轉, 要作從長計議!!今日無謂戀戰!!","createTime":"2019-08-11T13:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T07:12:08.000Z","uid":110509,"like":427,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"e70b67e47f1077f86a50077aa269cc679270aa5a","tid":1444773,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:13:13.000Z","msg":"希望咁多位手足11點前返晒屋企!! <br />\n最多最多快閃多一個地方 就要返屋企!!<br />\n<br />\n琴日同今日,<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警係玩快撃</span>, 每次黑警出擊都有個手足被捕<br />\n例如: <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">(1) 速龍由私家車飛落黎狂跑捉人<br />\n(2) 有鬼係前線, 速龍跑黎時就按住手足,唔俾佢走<br />\n(3) 放煙霧彈等你救火, 再乘機出速龍狂跑捉人</span><br />\n<br />\n今日已經捉左好多好多好多人喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望咁多位先退一退, 總結一下, 再諗之後用咩戰術應對先<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 個POST可能好多正評, 因為現場未必人人都回到POST.  <br />\n不過都希望前線們可以參考, 今日先退, 明日再出都未遲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325604765cee3d12d75af4263885d9ac58c1bbf2","tid":1444773,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:13:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a61194433759f1fe17c44ae7d3ce1849b3420dbf","tid":1444773,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:14:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"714e14f6ea38f6fb17c393c3ca721d6c747491a5","tid":1444773,"uid":110509,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:14:40.000Z","msg":"今日先退, 明日再出都未遲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返黎再計劃下先, 唔好送無謂既頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75f10f3c3ced6ce55750bd66bf9ac26560cbaec","tid":1444773,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:15:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cec0c6a04fd5c4bdb7fd941b3ed385491f912034","tid":1444773,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,